findings.fix:
Pre-group cards once with useMemo:
```
const cardsByDate = useMemo(() => {
  const m = new Map<string, ContentCard[]>();
  for (const c of cards) if (c.scheduledDate) {
    const arr = m.get(c.scheduledDate) ?? [];
    arr.push(c);
    m.set(c.scheduledDate, arr);
  }
  return m;
}, [cards]);
```
Then `cardsByDate.get(dateStr) ?? EMPTY`. Apply to both calendar-page.tsx and the MiniCalendar in dashboard-page.tsx.

